# CCE Demo
Output docs/demo.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 960
Set Height 540
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 35ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.5

# Init
Type "cd /tmp/cce-demo"
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "cce init"
Enter
Sleep 12s

# Search
Type "cce search 'how does authentication work'"
Enter
Sleep 5s

# Savings
Type "cce savings"
Enter
Sleep 4s

# Banner
Type "cce"
Enter
Sleep 4s
